reviews.review_text:
One of the high points in R&R history That point in the Stella Blue outro jam when all reality is suspended and we all get to feel what it was like before the fall.  Time and space where I could spend eternity.  That is why I went to so many of these shows, searching for those specific cracks in the veneer of reality.   This show was chuck full of them.   The whole second set.  I was at this show and it saved my life.  Set my course for the next 10 years...

This version is strong, in your face, wild and crazy.  Even at the time the 1st set didn't do much for me, but the second set starts at full throttle.  I enjoy this recording more than the others,  it gives a better feel for the experience at the show.
